title: Carrie Underwood Releases Another New Song 'Renegade Runaway'
text:
Comments The 'American Idol' alum releases another fresh track ahead of the release of her new studio album 'Storyteller'. 
Carrie Underwood continues to roll out new song to hype up the upcoming release of her next studio installment, " Storyteller ". A week before the album arrives in stores, she drops a fresh track called "Renegade Runaway". The " American Idol " alum is scheduled to release her fifth studio album in the United States on October 23. It's her first LP since 2012's " Blown Away ". She has so far released at least three songs ahead of the album release. Carrie Underwood is among the musicians tapped to pay tribute to Frank Sinatra for his 100th birthday. She is joined by John Legend , Usher , Adam Levine , Alicia Keys , Tony Bennett , and Garth Brooks . The concert will be taped on December 2 at Wynn Las Vegas' Encore Theatre and broadcast December 6 on CBS.
